<event name="ROCK_APOLOGY" unique="true">
	<ship load="SHIP_ROCK_GENERIC" hostile="false"/>
	<text>Moments after entering the system, you receive a message from the nearby ship; "We are sinners! Oh woe is us! Strike us down! Punish us! We do not deserve the gift of life!"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ask them why they're upset.</text>
		<event load="ROCK_APOLOGY_INTERROGATE"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Strike them down.</text>
		<event load="ROCK_APOLOGY_ATTACK"/>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ignore them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The Rockman's pleading continues for some time, but you simply tune them out and fly away.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
				<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
			</choice>
			<choice>
				<text>Do nothing.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>
<eventList name="ROCK_APOLOGY_INTERROGATE">
    <event>
        <text>"I have SINNED! I... used the restroom... and I was out of toilet paper... and I had a holy script nearby and... OH GOD! I'm a MONSTER! How could you make me relive my crimes? You are cruel! Too cruel for this world! First I will kill you, then myself!"</text>
        <ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>계속...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
    </event>
    <event>
        <text>"I have SINNED! I... used the restroom... and I was out of toilet paper... and I had a holy script nearby and... OH GOD! I'm a MONSTER! Oh please, allow me to redeem myself! In any way I can, perhaps there are favors I can serve to find my way to heaven once more!"</text>
		<crewMember amount="1" class="rock"/>
	</event>
</eventList>
<eventList name="ROCK_APOLOGY_ATTACK">
    <event>
        <text>"I have changed my mind! I no longer wish to die! I shall redeem myself by killing you instead!"</text>
        <ship hostile="true"/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>계속...</text>
			<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
		</choice>
    </event>
    <event>
        <text>"Oh thank you good captain! Only in death shall I find redemption!"</text>
		<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
		<enemyDamage amount="30"/>
	</event>
</eventList>

<event name="ROCK_PUNS" unique="true">
	<ship load="SHIP_ROCK_GENERIC" hostile="false"/>
	<text>A stoic Rock Captain hails you. "Federation. I have an important question for you. Why can you not expect perfection from geologists?"</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Uh... We don't know.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Because they all have their FAULTS!" He breaks into intense laughter.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Laugh in return.</text>
				<event>
					<text>Your laughter mixes together with the Rockman. After a while, you both calm down. So grateful that you found humor in his pun, the Rockman feels compelled to gift you some missiles!</text>
					<autoReward level="MED">missiles_only</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>End their pitiful existence.</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Wait... Wait no, it was just a joke!"</text>
					<ship hostile="true"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>계속...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_ZOLTAN">
				<text>(Zoltan Crew) "What a shocker!"</text>
				<event>
					<text>The Rockman is so impressed by the retaliation of your own pun that he submits, promising to dedicate the rest of his existence to your servitude. As long as he can keep making puns along the way.</text>
					<crewMember amount="1" class="rock">Comedian</crewMember>
					<autoReward level="MED">missiles_only</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_CRYSTAL">
				<text>(Crystal Crew) "Ahh, a wise crack!"</text>
				<event>
					<text>The Rockman is so impressed by the retaliation of your own pun that he submits, promising to dedicate the rest of his existence to your servitude. As long as he can keep making puns along the way.</text>
					<crewMember amount="1" class="rock">Comedian</crewMember>
					<autoReward level="MED">missiles_only</autoReward>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true" req="LIST_CREW_LEECH">
				<text>(Leech Crew) "That joke sucks."</text>
				<event>
					<text>"Is that supposed to be a pun? I cannot tell if you are insulting me or making a pitiful attempt to join me. I hate Leeches. Get out of my sight!"</text>
					<ship hostile="true"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>계속...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="LIST_CREW_SLUG" hidden="true">
		<text>(Slug Crew) Have your Slug predict the answer.</text>
		<event>
			<text>Your Slug grumbles. "It'ssss jussst a ssstupid pun." Your Slug repeats the answer to the Rockmen. "Because they all have faultssss..." The Rockman frowns that you predicted it, and turns off transmissions.</text>
		</event>
	</choice>
</event>

