	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>What prophecy?</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Have you not heard? The ship from a future much brighter than ours, who will bring about a great change! A gift from the high heavens, bestowed upon us mortal-bound men by the benevolent Crystal ones!"</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Could we be the ship from the prophecy?</text>
				<event>
					<text>One of the Rockmen pull down their cloak and stare for a long time deep into your eyes. "I am no expert, but you have the look of a creature driven by a force beyond your control. Your will is bent by a being from the great beyond, manipulated for the simple sake of amusement. If you are not the one spoken of in the prophecy, then surely you are important regardless. Perhaps this may be of aid."</text>
