				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>These people are crazy, let's leave.</text>
				<event/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Ignore them.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You have better things to than listen to the ravings of these religious loons.</text>
			<choice>
				<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
