<textList name="TEXT_ENCOUNTER_ROCKHOME">
	<text>You catch chatter on the nearby Rock ship. In a hush tone, they speak of your ship and what vile sins must be committed aboard it. Eager to enact out the Elders' law, they power up weapons and attack!</text>
	<text>The Rock citizens are perhaps some of the best armed civilians of any race. Unfortunately, that means just about every ship you encounter here is more than willing to engage you in a brawl.</text>
	<text>You've stepped foot in the Rock Homeworlds, the highly valued sanctuary for the Rock people. It is no wonder that the irate citizens of this sector seek your destruction so eagerly.</text>
	<text>"This one, he is not covered in stone! We shall cut off his head, and mount it to our wall as a trophy!" It doesn't seem the Rockmen here are willing to negotiate.</text>
	<text>There is a very thin line between civilians and military in the Rock Homeworlds. It's hard to tell the origins of the ship here, but nevertheless they're hostile and looking for a fight.</text>
	<text>Your very presence in this sector is a tremendous insult to Rock-kind. The Rockmen in the nearby system aren't pleased with your presence and decide to deal with you themselves.</text>
	<text>Rockmen aren't particularly friendly, but you know you've made a real mistake coming here when the civilians near this beacon go out of their way to initiate combat with you.</text>
</textList>

<event name="ENCOUNTER_INQUISITION" unique="true">
	<text>The Rockman Crusaders were once recruited to enact the Inquisition, a brutal invasion of other worlds deemed full of heretics and instate the 'wisdom' of the Elders. The Federation has since put an end to the Inquisition, but the Crusader rank has not yet been disbanded. Now, they patrol the homeworlds as Elites and protect them from outsiders, such as yourself.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_ROCK_ELITE_FIGHT" hostile="true"/> 
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>계속...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>

<event name="ENCOUNTER_LOSTSUN_ROCKHOME" unique="true">
	<text>A Lost Sun ship, seeking out Rock citizens to capture and take back to the Stronghold as prisoners, identifies your ship. "Traitorous coward! A Federation vessel, out here, giving aid to the Rock Elders' followers? You are scum! I will roast all of you alive with only the holiest of fire." They aren't exactly correct, but you doubt arguing will help.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_LOSTSUN_FIGHT" hostile="true"/> 
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>계속...</text>
		<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
	</choice>
</event>

