            <text>On your screen appears a lavishly dressed Crystal painted gold sitting aboard a jagged command chair chiseled out of citrine. "Ah, so someone has finally responded. You foreigners are quite... erm... nevermind. Salutations! I am Sir Ruwen Argote, standing Foreign Ambassador of the Great Crystalline Empire. I have been sent here by her majesty Empress Dianesh Kryel. Quite a mouthful of names, yes? I understand you foreigners just love to share your names with all that you meet. Strange, strange... oh, but please take no offense!"</text>
