<event name="RUWEN_ENCOUNTER_MISSION">
	<text>Ruwen glances at his forearm where an ornate digital watch sits upon his wrist and projects the time into the air. "Erm, yes, sorry. Ycathine's crypt knows, I've gotten carried away with my ramblings again. Where was I? Oh, yes. I have been sent here by Empress Dianesh on an important diplomatic mission to recover a sacred object! Very boring political stuff, you wouldn't care much about it. But what you might care about is a job offer! I am in need of an escort. As you can see, my ship is very poorly armed. I require a ship that is... hum, how to put it... ready to put the fecal matter back up the rectums of those who stand in its path? I think that is how you foreigners say it?"</text>
