            <text>You fly through the city, taking in truly just how massive it is, compared to all of the much smaller Outcast villages you've seen. As a newcomer and a renegade you are welcomed warmly, and your time in the city is a pleasant one. You meet a humble Aquarian fisherman who convinces you to try a sample of some exotic octopus, an exceptionally elderly Orchid Chieftain whom crafts dreamcatchers from his own twigs, and even share an awkward encounter with a very drunken ex-Rebel who claims to be Admiral Vance's long lost brother, who buys you 3 rounds of drinks before passing out. You also find a number of stores selling military supplies with an incredible variety of items to choose from.</text>
			<store>STORE_TURBAN</store>
