<event name="TURBAN_BOMBING_COALITION">
	<text>There is a palpable feeling of unease in the room, but every attempt to break the tension goes nowhere. Through the silence you can hear the distant thuds and feel the violent shaking as the bombardment of the city above continues without relent. At this rate, nothing will be left. Hours pass, and you're certain the fleet is making progress on your location. Several times footsteps can be heard outside the room, but no one ever enters.</text>
	<modifyPursuit amount="1"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
